WEBVTT

01:22.972 --> 01:29.213
"While he was still speaking,
Judas, one of the Twelve, arrived.

01:29.980 --> 01:32.950
With him was a large crowd
with swords

01:32.983 --> 01:36.820
and clubs from the chief priests
and the elders of the people.

01:38.022 --> 01:41.692
Now the betrayer
had given them a sign saying,

01:41.724 --> 01:45.696
'The one I kiss is the man,
arrest him.'

01:47.298 --> 01:51.835
At once he came up to Jesus
and said, 'Greetings, Rabbi,

01:51.868 --> 01:53.471
and kissed him.'

01:54.537 --> 01:59.977
Jesus said to him, 'Friend,
do what you are here to do.'

02:01.644 --> 02:05.682
Then they came and laid hands
on Jesus and arrested him.

02:05.715 --> 02:09.887
Suddenly, one of those with
Jesus put his hands on his sword,

02:09.919 --> 02:13.957
drew it and struck the slave of the
high priest cutting off his ear.

02:15.025 --> 02:19.830
Then Jesus said to him,
'Put your sword back into its place,

02:19.862 --> 02:23.568
for all who live by the sword
shall die by the sword.

02:24.501 --> 02:27.405
Do you think that
I cannot call on my Father,

02:27.437 --> 02:31.608
and he will at once send me more
than twelve legions of angels?

02:32.575 --> 02:36.013
But how then would
the Scriptures be fulfilled

02:36.045 --> 02:40.450
which say it must happen
in this way?'"

02:51.427 --> 02:56.533
Throughout your life, people
will come to persecute you.

02:58.102 --> 03:01.038
They will tell you
that you're doing evil,

03:01.070 --> 03:03.507
that your actions
are causing harm

03:03.539 --> 03:07.679
and that everything
you believe is falsehood.

03:10.681 --> 03:12.517
All this happened to Jesus.

03:14.050 --> 03:19.756
And when they came to persecute Jesus,
he knew it was his Father's will.

03:21.758 --> 03:26.663
He knew that it was going
to be okay in the end,

03:28.465 --> 03:32.069
and that this trial
was temporary.

03:33.903 --> 03:37.574
And he knew that to fight
against his attackers

03:37.608 --> 03:40.378
would be to go against
God's plan.

03:42.513 --> 03:45.849
If you fight hate with hate,

03:47.850 --> 03:49.787
who really wins in the end?

03:51.854 --> 03:55.792
If you don't love your enemies,

03:55.825 --> 03:58.829
can you really call yourself
a Christian?

04:01.965 --> 04:05.936
If you don't put away your sword

04:05.968 --> 04:08.739
when they come to crucify you,

04:09.772 --> 04:14.144
how can you still stand
among the angels?

05:24.514 --> 05:25.582
Hmm.

05:26.583 --> 05:28.919
Think you can add to it?

05:28.951 --> 05:32.223
It's already 600 words
on a high school baseball team.

05:33.189 --> 05:34.925
The boy hit a grand slam.

05:34.958 --> 05:38.762
And they still lost.
Besides, he gives shit quotes.

05:38.795 --> 05:41.466
Yeah, he's not
particularly loquacious.

05:42.865 --> 05:45.002
