05:45.035 --> 05:48.806
- Na, I'll make it work.
- It already works.

05:51.240 --> 05:52.942
- Hey, Dani.
- Yeah.

05:52.975 --> 05:56.213
That story about the
new home church, can I have it?

05:57.915 --> 05:59.950
