to remain silent during services,

11:34.583 --> 11:37.186
that's in the Bible, right?

11:37.220 --> 11:39.956
Yes, those are God's words.

11:39.990 --> 11:42.292
"God's words."

11:42.325 --> 11:47.064
Is that how you justify the stoning of a
divorced woman in one of your Ohio outlets?

11:47.096 --> 11:49.131
I don't have to justify
anything to you.

11:49.164 --> 11:50.867
