gay people.

11:56.306 --> 12:01.211
What passage did you pull from exactly when
you decided to burn that gay couple's house?

12:01.244 --> 12:05.548
Those sinners
got what they deserved.

12:05.581 --> 12:10.553
Adulterers and sodomites
have no place in God's house.

12:12.589 --> 12:14.558
God hates
all forms of wickedness,

12:14.591 --> 12:18.596
especially those who think
they're above His chosen leaders.

12:20.663 --> 12:21.966
Okay.

13:07.677 --> 13:13.050
Fine, leave. You'll be back.
You always come back.

13:29.331 --> 13:31.668
Did you only bring one of these?

13:31.701 --> 13:35.038
- What more do you want from me, heh?
- Fuck.

13:35.071 --> 13:37.574
I'm gonna need like four more
if I'm gonna get through this.

13:37.606 --> 13:40.009
Okay, well, you asked for it.

13:40.043 --> 13:42.144
Well,
I didn't think she'd make me go back.

13:42.177 --> 13:44.347
You really thought Dani was just
gonna let you write an article

13:44.380 --> 13:46.482
shitting all over
the new church?

13:47.417 --> 13:48.285
You wanna come with me?

13:50.220 --> 13:53.123
No, I have to go to work and
besides, it won't be that bad.

13:53.155 --> 13:55.591
I mean,
how bad could it be?

13:55.625 --> 13:59.062
And, hey,
maybe Thomas will be there.

13:59.095 --> 14:02.165
- Uh, yeah, I highly doubt that.
- Oh, why not?

14:02.197 --> 14:03.699
Have you not talked to him?

14:03.732 --> 14:05.668
Well, no,
we didn't exchange numbers.

14:05.701 --> 14:08.705
Besides,
he's probably long gone.

14:08.738 --> 14:11.108
Well, whatever.

14:11.140 --> 14:14.211
I can hook you up with one of Sunset
Acres' most eligible bachelors.

14:14.244 --> 14:18.048
I can think of at least two
who've only groped me like once.

14:18.081 --> 14:20.616
Okay, I get it.
My job's not that bad.

14:20.649 --> 14:25.355
Yeah, heh. Well, if you change your mind, you
can always come work for me as a nurse's aide.

14:25.388 --> 14:28.091
