15:17.273 --> 15:20.543
Uh, do you have a bathroom?

15:40.163 --> 15:41.632
Hey.

15:45.434 --> 15:46.502
Thomas.

15:46.535 --> 15:48.604
Sorry, you walked in on that.

15:50.206 --> 15:51.642
So what's up?

15:54.510 --> 15:56.379
So is this why you couldn't
come in the other night?

15:56.412 --> 15:58.415
No, no,
Georgine is not a thing.

15:58.447 --> 16:00.250
