on religion?

16:04.854 --> 16:06.889
Okay, well, you also said you
weren't gonna be in town long.

16:06.923 --> 16:08.424
Yeah, that part's true.

16:08.457 --> 16:10.826
I'm moving to the next town as soon
as we're established here, all right.

16:10.860 --> 16:12.495
My brother's gonna
take over the church here.

16:12.528 --> 16:13.830
I'm just here to help get
the ball rolling.

16:13.863 --> 16:15.799
Right. Okay.

16:15.831 --> 16:18.134
You're not gonna tell anyone,
right?

16:19.568 --> 16:21.403
No, I'm not gonna tell on you.

16:21.437 --> 16:23.539
From what I could see,
it was all consensual,

16:23.572 --> 16:26.175
which is kind of a rarity
for you guys, so...

16:26.208 --> 16:30.713
Yeah, and it's been at the center
of some pretty fucked up shit.

16:30.746 --> 16:33.582
Okay.
So, why are you a part of it?

16:33.615 --> 16:35.718
