I know you're not that shallow.

16:37.452 --> 16:39.688
It's the only thing I've...
I've known, all right,

16:39.721 --> 16:42.424
plus it gives me a platform
that I wouldn't have otherwise.

16:42.457 --> 16:47.697
So I try to use that platform to do
as much good in the world as I can.

16:49.532 --> 16:52.402
From everything I know about Emeth,
I don't see how that's possible.

16:53.970 --> 16:56.139
You have to keep an open mind.

16:58.875 --> 17:00.809
You know,
some people fuck in beds.

17:00.842 --> 17:02.544
You know I'd heard that.

17:02.577 --> 17:05.882
Problem is the bathroom is the only room in
the house that doesn't have a camera in it.

17:05.914 --> 17:07.716
- What?
- Yeah.

17:07.750 --> 17:11.253
Father put cameras in all
the rooms except the bathrooms.

17:11.287 --> 17:13.355
He says it's to keep an eye
on his congregation,

17:13.388 --> 17:16.692
but really I think it's just
to keep the leadership in line

17:16.726 --> 17:20.664
from all those non-consensual
acts you mentioned,

17:20.696 --> 17:23.532
which is sad really, you know.

17:23.566 --> 17:25.769
People do whatever
they want when God's watching,

17:25.801 --> 17:28.871
but as soon as they figure out
others are watching,

17:28.904 --> 17:31.208
they change their behavior
entirely.

17:32.541 --> 17:34.810
This is all off the record,
by the way.

17:34.844 --> 17:38.847
Hmm. Shame. Would have made
a fascinating angle.

17:48.324 --> 17:50.826
Welcome.
Welcome to all of you.

17:52.528 --> 17:56.599
I would now like to introduce our
founder and our shepherd of Emeth.

17:56.633 --> 17:58.835
And he can't be here for long

17:58.867 --> 18:01.770
because he has many other places to go
to help spread the ministry of Emeth.

18:01.804 --> 18:05.509
But we have him here today,
which is the greatest blessing of all.

18:06.608 --> 18:07.711
Father...

18:17.920 --> 18:19.489
Welcome.

18:20.722 --> 18:22.358
Welcome all of you.

18:23.692 --> 18:27.698
God has brought
all of you here...

18:30.432 --> 18:35.739
and God wants
all of you to be here.

18:35.771 --> 18:40.843
And I can't wait to see
what he has in store for you,

18:41.943 --> 18:43.413
here at Emeth.

18:46.883 --> 18:48.619
It won't be easy.

18:50.787 --> 18:54.290
God never promised
that life would be easy,

18:55.325 --> 18:58.628
but it is ultimately

18:58.661 --> 19:01.664
the only way to happiness,

19:02.964 --> 19:05.534
to gaining His favor

19:06.903 --> 19:09.506
and eternal life with Him.

19:18.815 --> 19:22.885
None of you
deserve to be here

19:25.587 --> 19:26.690
for you...

19:26.722 --> 19:31.028
We, are all sinners.

19:32.894 --> 19:36.833
But there is hope,

19:38.534 --> 19:41.104
hope eternal

19:41.136 --> 19:45.442
for even the wickedest
of sinners.

19:45.474 --> 19:49.511
Together through fellowship

19:49.545 --> 19:51.315
and accountability,

19:52.481 --> 19:54.550
we can ensure

19:54.584 --> 19:59.355
that we reach paradise together

19:59.388 --> 20:03.326
and inspire others to join us.

20:05.560 --> 20:06.696
Hmm.

20:11.733 --> 20:12.901
We're lucky.

20:14.737 --> 20:20.710
We have a book
that tells us exactly

20:20.742 --> 20:25.014
what we need to do
in order to please Him.

20:26.048 --> 20:28.050
Simple rules,

20:28.084 --> 20:31.955
but rules that the world calls

20:31.988 --> 20:34.691
ludicrous fairytales.

20:37.460 --> 20:40.364
Politically incorrect,

20:42.898 --> 20:45.033
outdated.

20:48.570 --> 20:50.039
I assure you,

20:51.106 --> 20:56.413
there is nothing
outdated about God.

20:57.180 --> 21:01.518
He is alive and well.

21:01.550 --> 21:05.154
And He is in this place.

21:06.689 --> 21:10.727
He is in this town.

21:13.729 --> 21:18.869
Like any father,
He demands obedience.

21:21.037 --> 21:25.909
He demands that marriage
be kept sacred,

21:27.609 --> 21:31.981
that we put nothing else
before Him,

21:33.015 --> 21:38.755
that our bodies
be kept His temple.

21:42.090 --> 21:43.759
Now in this town,

21:46.561 --> 21:48.998
there is divorce,

21:50.199 --> 21:56.006
there are people
who don't put God first.

21:57.573 --> 22:01.811
There is extramarital sex,

22:01.844 --> 22:03.779
homosexuality,

22:03.813 --> 22:07.517
and children born
out of wedlock.

22:09.719 --> 22:13.623
All of these things
are an abomination to God

22:13.655 --> 22:16.658
and those that do these things,
He abhors them

22:16.692 --> 22:21.163
and He has stricken their name
from the book of life.

22:27.970 --> 22:29.472
But...

22:31.907 --> 22:37.779
there is a way
to get our name

22:37.813 --> 22:40.951
back in that book.

22:45.555 --> 22:49.926
And that is what
we're here to do.

23:05.141 --> 23:10.013
