whole fucking thing, guilty by association.

23:27.296 --> 23:28.632
Look you...

23:30.333 --> 23:34.202
You learn to justify stupid opinions like
that or at least you learn to ignore them.

23:34.236 --> 23:37.640
It's hard to leave something
I've known my entire life.

23:40.241 --> 23:42.645
